---
layout: base.njk
title: "About Us"
description: "Learn the story of Gomer Faith Ministries, meet Pastor Michael and Elder Pauline Lewis, and read our vision, mission, and safeguarding commitments."
nav: about
permalink: /about/
---
<section class="hero" style="padding-bottom:60px;">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="eyebrow">Our story</span>
    <h1>{{ about.hero_headline }}</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="max-width:60ch;">{{ about.hero_text }}</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container two-col">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Vision</span>
      <h2>{{ about.vision_headline }}</h2>
      <p class="lead">{{ about.vision_text }}</p>
    </div>
    <div class="stack reveal">
      {% for point in homepage.mission_points %}
      <div class="info-item"><span class="label">{{ point.label }}</span>{{ point.text }}</div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dim">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="center reveal" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto 48px;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Leadership</span>
      <h2>Meet our leaders</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-2 reveal">
      {% for leader in collections.leaders %}
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-art"><img src="{{ leader.data.image }}" alt="{{ leader.data.name }}" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <h3>{{ leader.data.name }}</h3>
          <p>{{ leader.templateContent | safe }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" id="safeguarding">
  <div class="container two-col">
    <div class="reveal">
      <span class="eyebrow">Safeguarding</span>
      <h2>{{ about.safeguarding_headline }}</h2>
      <p class="lead">{{ about.safeguarding_text }}</p>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/contact/">Contact our safeguarding lead →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stack reveal">
      <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Trained leaders</span>All children's and youth workers are briefed on safeguarding practice.</div>
      <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Clear reporting</span>Concerns can be raised directly with our safeguarding lead at any time.</div>
      <div class="info-item"><span class="label">Ongoing review</span>Our safeguarding approach is reviewed regularly against current guidance.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section--dim">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="next-step reveal">
      <div>
        <h2>Want to know more?</h2>
        <p>We'd love to tell you more about where Gomer came from and where it's headed.</p>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/contact/">Get in Touch</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
